WEBVTT

00:00:00.444 --> 00:00:02.103
Track 06.07

00:00:03.955 --> 00:00:06.026
Meg: Would you like a cup of coffee, Rob?

00:00:06.389 --> 00:00:07.804
Rob: Yes, please.

00:00:08.436 --> 00:00:10.341
Meg: And would you like a piece of cake?

00:00:10.539 --> 00:00:13.899
Rob: No, I’m fine, thanks – just coffee, please.

00:00:14.336 --> 00:00:17.072
Meg: I need to make lunch for Jake and Carrie.

00:00:17.522 --> 00:00:18.388
Rob: I’ll help you.

00:00:18.543 --> 00:00:22.346
Meg: All right. Thanks. We need pizzas.

00:00:22.601 --> 00:00:24.160
Rob: I can make pizzas.

00:00:24.385 --> 00:00:26.527
I make very good pizzas!

00:00:26.633 --> 00:00:28.465
Meg: Don’t worry. It’s OK.

00:00:28.716 --> 00:00:31.282
The pizzas at the supermarket are fine.

00:00:31.514 --> 00:00:34.247
Rob: OK, I’ll go to the supermarket.

00:00:34.434 --> 00:00:36.789
Meg: Thank you. That’s great.